{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_02_02",
  "title": "井川葵",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "愛に元気がないから、ちょっと話してあげてくれないか\nあぁすずは一番頼りになるから。ありがとう。じゃあ",
      "startTime": 5.333333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6266.666666666667,
          "startTime": 11.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……随分あっさりと引き受けてくれたね",
      "startTime": 11.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ見えて\n面倒見がいいからな、すずは",
      "startTime": 16.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "一番頼りになるとか言って\n持ち上げてたじゃないか。君も策士だな",
      "startTime": 20.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや本当に頼りになるんだって\n明るいし、精神的にもタフなんだよ",
      "startTime": 28.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、いいのかな\n彼女を、僕達の、LizNoirの問題に巻き込んで",
      "startTime": 34.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "同じ事務所にはなったけど、彼女達にとって\n僕達はライバルでもある。申し訳ないよ",
      "startTime": 43.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "葵、初めてうちの子達――\nさくらと琴乃に会った日のことを覚えているか？",
      "startTime": 51.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、三枝さんに会いに行って\n二人に会ったね",
      "startTime": 57.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "まだ、サニピも月ストも結成前だったんだっけ？\nあの頃は二人ともまだまだだったな",
      "startTime": 63.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、葵と莉央さんが彼女達の前で踊ってくれたろ\nあれは凄く刺激になったんだ",
      "startTime": 72.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それからだよ、二人がより一層レッスンに力を\n入れ出したのは。二人も、もちろん俺も感謝している",
      "startTime": 78.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか\nでも、僕達は全然そんなつもりはなかったんだけど",
      "startTime": 87.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "葵、君はとてもしっかりしている。自分の芯を持った\n強い子だ。でも、だからこそ覚えてほしいことがある",
      "startTime": 96.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "……何を？",
      "startTime": 102.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "周りの人に、もっと頼っていいってことをだ",
      "startTime": 104.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "……周りの人に頼る……",
      "startTime": 109.03333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、だから、今回のことは俺とすずに頼ってくれ",
      "startTime": 114.53333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……分かったよ。君とすずに期待させてもらう\n実は僕も彼女は嫌いじゃないんだ",
      "startTime": 127.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "しゃべり方が面白い子だと思ってたら\n中身はもっと面白いからね",
      "startTime": 134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "葵の嫌いじゃない、は好きって意味だよな？",
      "startTime": 136.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "……うるさいよ",
      "startTime": 141.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 146.93333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "どうだい？　僕と莉央が考えた四人体制の新しい\n『The Last Chance』の振り付けだよ",
      "startTime": 154.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "四人一緒じゃないから、分かりにくいかもだけど\n先に君の意見を聞きたいんだ",
      "startTime": 160.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "悪くないと思うけど、ソロのダンスパートは？",
      "startTime": 162.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "愛が前に出て、他のメンバーがサイドに回る\n新メンバーにそれぞれ見せ場があるんだ",
      "startTime": 169.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの人達にもっと、愛とこころを知ってもらいたい\nそのための構成さ",
      "startTime": 177.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか、優しい先輩だな",
      "startTime": 179.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだか、不服そうだね\n言いたいことがあるなら、はっきり言ってくれないか",
      "startTime": 186.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "君と僕の間に遠慮なんていらない",
      "startTime": 189.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、愛と莉央さんで前に出た方がよくないか？\nダンスのクオリティを重視すると、俺はそう感じるんだ",
      "startTime": 199.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "……さすがだね\n実は僕もそう思ってたんだ",
      "startTime": 205.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
